      "$value": "Ferrari custom sans-serif",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Single weight 400 typeface used for everything — navigation, headlines, body, labels. All-caps headlines and nav with aggressive positive tracking (0.083–0.091em) is the signature move; body copy uses near-zero or slightly positive tracking (0.015–0.028em). Absence of bold/light weights is a deliberate editorial choice: hierarchy is created by size and tracking, never weight contrast."
    }
  },
